630
01:17:30,396 --> 01:17:31,397
Fous le camp !

631
01:17:31,814 --> 01:17:32,648
Pars maintenant.

632
01:17:33,107 --> 01:17:34,108
Pars !

633
01:17:34,692 --> 01:17:36,068
Fous le camp !

634
